  <brief_title>Study to Determine the Effect of Food on the Absorption of an Oral Testosterone Undecanoate Formulation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase II Study of the Effect of Food With Various Levels of Fat on the Pharmacokinetics of an Oral Testosterone Undecanoate Formulation in Hypogonadal Men</official_title>
  <sponsors>
